{"tid":1668098,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【Sulli雪莉逝世】IU為推遲新專輯面世致歉：老實說我需要些時間","createTime":"2019-10-21T22:25:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T00:32:40.000Z","uid":34643,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"89e429fd6ce1928e74f95a54a1f4bf9a47e59e74","tid":1668098,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T22:25:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3434077/org/1f3f12aac90f342c9315f3bf1d06054c.jpg/y1bI98JSRMVnFevrhhd8z5YACw_APaAhQ3EwEENxMBA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3434077%2Forg%2F1f3f12aac90f342c9315f3bf1d06054c.jpg%2Fy1bI98JSRMVnFevrhhd8z5YACw_APaAhQ3EwEENxMBA&h=6f1e6655&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSulli雪莉本月14日突然離世，並於17日低調出殯。（視覺中國）<br />\n<br />\nIU原定本月28日公開《Love Poem》專輯同名歌曲， 11月1日發行專輯，並在11月2至3日於光州舉行同名演唱會，惟受雪莉離世影響，IU決定推遲發行專輯，而《Love Poem》一曲屬演唱會表演曲目之一，因此將改於11月1日率先面世。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3434074/org/8da5d3916117dfda3aa2e2bf2ac1ae41.jpg/yfpd2tEAmLTptRAgB6zsiYHhEXhuBvA1ICcDpyAnA6c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3434074%2Forg%2F8da5d3916117dfda3aa2e2bf2ac1ae41.jpg%2Fyfpd2tEAmLTptRAgB6zsiYHhEXhuBvA1ICcDpyAnA6c&h=f31c3db4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nIU與雪莉份屬好友，所以雪莉的離世令IU大受打擊。（IG/@jin_ri_sul，帳號現已刪除）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3434075/org/7c069e0fe90df8f388fd0af163f6b9c4.jpg/SHfm_aUsbyumvkLMuPn8FoI2eTADh9qtji_APo4vwD4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3434075%2Forg%2F7c069e0fe90df8f388fd0af163f6b9c4.jpg%2FSHfm_aUsbyumvkLMuPn8FoI2eTADh9qtji_APo4vwD4&h=d2f52f8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nIU原定11月1日推出的新專輯《Love Poem》，現時受好友離世影響延期推出。（IU官方Facebook）<br />\n<br />\nIU在文章坦言：「距離同名演出還有2星期左右的時間，所以就演出的整體訊息、歌單等問題和工作人員一起苦惱了很久，但老實說，我個人需要一些時間&hellip;&hellip;作為專輯製作人和製作演出的歌手，今次肩負很重的責任感，（但是）我個人力量無法支撐，我比任何人都熱切期待我的新作品，真的非常抱歉。」IU又承諾不會讓歌迷等新專輯等太久，亦不會送上令人失望的演出。"},{"pid":"c32fc895c2abac912ad6f02bd8c284b74630ddcf","tid":1668098,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T22:26:31.000Z","msg":"Old news"},{"pid":"9b0e7d13d55d2418737b51a7ec2cf8817c8efc12","tid":1668098,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T23:14:15.000Z","msg":"聽住舊歌頂住先<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OPHOJhema3c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOPHOJhema3c&d=kAMrkm0lh8tAzahNx%2FKaSIvgSq%2BgcR%2FX%2FBaLnjou7zI%3D&h=11857c12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OPHOJhema3c</a>"},{"pid":"572bc62f744d4da0d51aa73c2fe41de2a75dac74","tid":1668098,"uid":43061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T23:18:53.000Z","msg":"人美心善李知恩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84bd28a66f359d1ad308953cf7513d690c8c32d0","tid":1668098,"uid":184570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T23:21:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a6cd65ee86da0289615afdcc46284ebd433e28e","tid":1668098,"uid":34643,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"572bc62f744d4da0d51aa73c2fe41de2a75dac74","tid":1668098,"uid":43061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T23:18:53.000Z","msg":"人美心善李知恩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T23:52:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn.newsen.com/newsen/news_photo/2019/01/10/201901100858312310_4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.newsen.com%2Fnewsen%2Fnews_photo%2F2019%2F01%2F10%2F201901100858312310_4.jpg&h=39a2fee7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"70fdd8f278f78b637acb9ce10d1849ee06cb9e11","tid":1668098,"uid":143768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T00:32:40.000Z","msg